{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be elegant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Prestige Properties</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #A52A2A; /* Brownish-Red */\n            --secondary-color: #D2B48C; /* Tan */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --accent-color: #8B4513; /* Darker Brown */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .property-listing {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 20px;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .property-card {\n            width: 300px;\n            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .property-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .property-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .property-details {\n            padding: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .property-details h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n        }\n\n        .property-details p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .property-card {\n                width: calc(50% - 20px);\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .property-card {\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Prestige Properties</h1>\n        <p>Your Vision. Our Expertise.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#listings\">Listings</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"listings\">\n            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-listing\">\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Luxury+Villa\" alt=\"Luxury Villa\">\n                    <div class=\"property-details\">\n                        <h3>Exquisite Waterfront Villa</h3>\n                        <p>5 Bedrooms, 6 Bathrooms, Stunning Ocean Views, Private Dock.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$5,500,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=City+Loft\" alt=\"City Loft\">\n                    <div class=\"property-details\">\n                        <h3>Chic Downtown Loft</h3>\n                        <p>2 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, Modern Design, City Skyline Views.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$1,200,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Suburban+Home\" alt=\"Suburban Home\">\n                    <div class=\"property-details\">\n                        <h3>Family Dream Home</h3>\n                        <p>4 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms, Spacious Backyard, Quiet Neighborhood.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$750,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <hr style=\"border: 0; height: 1px; background-color: #e0e0e0; margin: 40px 0;\">\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Prestige Properties</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                Prestige Properties is a premier real estate brokerage dedicated to helping you find your perfect home or investment.\n                With years of experience in the market, our team of dedicated professionals offers unparalleled service, market insights,\n                and a commitment to achieving your real estate goals. We believe in building lasting relationships based on trust,\n                integrity, and exceptional results.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <hr style=\"border: 0; height: 1px; background-color: #e0e0e0; margin: 40px 0;\">\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                Have questions or ready to start your property search? We're here to help.\n                <br><br>\n                <strong>Email:</strong> info@prestigeproperties.com\n                <br>\n                <strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890\n                <br>\n                <strong>Address:</strong> 123 Red Oak Avenue, Suite 100, Cityville, ST 54321\n            </p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Prestige Properties. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}